<subSubSection pageId="14" pageNumber="2341" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="14.[160,1155,248,378]" box="[160,262,248,274]" pageId="14" pageNumber="2341">
<heading box="[160,262,248,274]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="14" pageNumber="2341" reason="5">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,262,248,274]" inLineHeading="true" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="2341" reason="3">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="14.[160,1155,248,378]" pageId="14" pageNumber="2341">
The species is close to 
<taxonomicName authority="Holmgren, 1858" authorityName="Holmgren" authorityYear="1858" box="[436,822,284,309]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Exochus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="2341" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ventralis">
<emphasis box="[436,626,284,309]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="2341">Exochus ventralis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Holmgren AE" box="[638,822,285,309]" pageId="14" pageNumber="2341" pagination="305 - 394" refId="ref17147" refString="Holmgren AE. 1858. Forsok till uppstallning och beskrifning af de i sverige funna Tryphonider (Monographia Tryphonidum Sueciae). Kongliga Svenska Vetenskapsakademiens Handlingar. N. F. 1: 305 - 394." type="book chapter" year="1858">Holmgren, 1858</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, but differs by not widened flagellum and elongated flagellomeres, not widened backward metasoma, more slender legs and coloration of the body.
</paragraph>
